{"tid":2081205,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮一度煞停 與參院磋商釋慮","createTime":"2020-06-27T05:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T06:36:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1d84a3f46a5add3fc93a8c8ad4d48db17ab361","tid":2081205,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200627/YXRDVBIA5XNRL5F26VJGO5X5N4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2FYXRDVBIA5XNRL5F26VJGO5X5N4%2F&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFhVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=25de2dd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2FYXRDVBIA5XNRL5F26VJGO5X5N4%2F&h=39680b6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200627/YXRDVBIA5XNRL5F26VJGO5X5N4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n白宮一度煞停 與參院磋商釋慮<br />\n<br />\n美國參議院一致通過《香港自治法案》後，需要眾議院通過和總統特朗普簽署，才會成為法律。民主黨控制的眾議院經常就人權問題向中國出手，通過法案料不成問題；而特朗普政府雖然對法案內容有保留，但議員相信磋商後已消除政府阻力。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：參議員：京最怕內地人看見自由<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hGLd7usZt3JmrRdOjQjhqRI8W64=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C6M5APUEXQBFA6WU5WNSAOCLLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhGLd7usZt3JmrRdOjQjhqRI8W64%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC6M5APUEXQBFA6WU5WNSAOCLLU.jpg&h=ec90257f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n修改細則令制裁時具彈性<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，由於《香港自治法案》設立強制制裁，特朗普政府官員曾有反對，指法案窒礙政府與中國進行外交的能力，亦在外交上給予國會太大權力。本月初加入成為法案共同提案人的共和黨參議員克拉默（Kevin Cramer，圖）表示，他上周三提出反對，令參議院無法一致通過法案而押後表決，是應白宮要求，讓政府可跟議員談判，以修改法案一些技術和政策問題。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》指出經磋商後<br />\n.............................<br />\n，可駁回總統豁免或中止制裁的決定。<br />\n<br />\n克拉默則表示，有<br />\n............................<br />\n令法案更有可能得到白宮肯首。<br />\n<br />\n《香港自治法案》的下一步將由眾議院審議表決，民主黨眾議員謝爾曼（Bradley Sherman）與共和黨眾議員約霍（Ted Yoho）已提交相應法案。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/美國《華爾街日報》"},{"pid":"6ce9d67bcc799c920cfec3a8506c483dc7812965","tid":2081205,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f51270db3964704aac4f455dadb94d9ecdfc36","tid":2081205,"uid":58612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"頂呢啲節錄真係睇撚死人，冇頭冇尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e631d2fcfe1cb5ed1e1e37efa21d0d3f3df681e","tid":2081205,"uid":235948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"44f51270db3964704aac4f455dadb94d9ecdfc36","tid":2081205,"uid":58612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"頂呢啲節錄真係睇撚死人，冇頭冇尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:36:44.000Z","msg":"去訂閱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}